title: Will you be a winner or a loser in Sydney's new bus plan?
text:
Will you be a winner or a loser in Sy... Will you be a winner or a loser in Sydney's new bus plan? 2 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
But some people will benefit, as their buses either take them closer to where they want to go or run more reliably. It is impossible to gauge exactly who these winners and losers will be before the changes start, but here is a stab.   Sydney Morning Herald.
